Class OrderOwner

java.lang.Object
org.team21.game.models.order.OrderOwner
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class OrderOwner extends Object implements Serializable
A class responsible for creating orders in the game. This class contains methods to generate different types of orders based on the input command.
Author:
Kapil Soni
